<code>&lt;slot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>L'élément <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML</a> <strong><code>&lt;menu&gt;</code></strong> est une alternative sémantique à <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a>, mais est traité par les navigateurs, et en termes d'accessibilité comme un élément <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a>. Il représente une liste d'éléments non-ordonnée (chaque élément de la liste étant représenté par un élément <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li\"><code>&lt;li&gt;</code></a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributs","title":"Attributs","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Cet élément inclut uniquement <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">les attributs universels</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes_dutilisation","title":"Notes d'utilisation","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Les éléments <code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> et <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a> représentent tous les deux une liste non-ordonnée d'éléments. <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a> doit être utilisés pour des éléments qui doivent uniquement être affichés alors que <code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> était initialement conçu pour des éléments interactifs.</p>\n<p>L'élément connexe <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menuitem\"><code>&lt;menuitem&gt;</code></a> a été déprécié.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note :</strong> Dans d'anciennes versions de la spécification HTML, l'élément <code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> pouvait être utilisé pour représenter un menu contextuel. Cette fonctionnalité est désormais considérée comme obsolète et ne fait plus partie de la spécification.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemples","title":"Exemples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"barre_doutils","title":"Barre d'outils","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Dans cet exemple, on utilise un élément <code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> afin de créer une barre d'outils pour une application d'édition.</p>\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onclick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">copy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Copier<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onclick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">cut</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Couper<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onclick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">paste</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Coller<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>On notera que, sur le plan fonctionnel, cela est équivalent à&nbsp;:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onclick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">copy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Copier<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onclick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">cut</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Couper<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onclick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">paste</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Coller<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"css\">CSS</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">menu, ul</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">list-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 400px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">li</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-grow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">button</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"résultat\">Résultat</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Barre d'outils\" id=\"frame_2537\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu/_sample_.2537.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"résumé_technique","title":"Résumé technique","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">Catégories de contenu</a></th>\n      <td><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#contenu_de_flux\">Contenu de flux</a> et <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#contenu_tangible\">contenu tangible</a> si au moins un enfant du menu est un élément <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li\"><code>&lt;li&gt;</code></a>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Contenu autorisé</th>\n      <td>Zéro ou plusieurs occurrences de <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li\"><code>&lt;li&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a>, et <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Omission de balises</th>\n      <td>Aucune balise ne doit être omise</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Parents autorisés</th>\n      <td>Tout élément qui accepte du <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#contenu_de_flux\">contenu de flux</a>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Rôle ARIA implicite</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/list_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">list (en-US)</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Rôles ARIA autorisés</th>\n      <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#directory\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>directory</code></a>, <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#group\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>group</code></a>, <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/listbox_role\"><code>listbox</code></a>, <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#menu\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>menu</code></a>, <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#menubar\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>menubar</code></a>, <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#none\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>none</code></a>, <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#presentation\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>presentation</code></a>, <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#radiogroup\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>radiogroup</code></a>, <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#tablist\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>tablist</code></a>, <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#toolbar\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>toolbar</code></a> ou <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#tree\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>tree</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Interface DOM</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMenuElement\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">HTMLMenuElement (en-US)</a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Spécifications","id":"spécifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/grouping-content.html#the-menu-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.menu"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.menu","dataURL":"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"voir_aussi","title":"Voir aussi","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Les autres éléments HTML relatifs aux listes&nbsp;:\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/li\"><code>&lt;li&gt;</code></a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Attributs","id":"attributs"},{"text":"Notes d'utilisation","id":"notes_dutilisation"},{"text":"Exemples","id":"exemples"},{"text":"Résumé technique","id":"résumé_technique"},{"text":"Spécifications","id":"spécifications"},{"text":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs"},{"text":"Voir aussi","id":"voir_aussi"}],"summary":"L'élément HTML <menu> est une alternative sémantique à <ul>, mais est traité par les navigateurs, et en termes d'accessibilité comme un élément <ul>. Il représente une liste d'éléments non-ordonnée (chaque élément de la liste étant représenté par un élément <li>).","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<menu>: The Menu element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"menu","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<menu>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<menu>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<menu>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<menu>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/html/element/menu","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/html/element/menu/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web","title":"Technologies web pour développeurs"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML (HyperText Markup Language)"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Référence des éléments HTML"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu","title":"<menu> : l'élément de menu"}],"pageTitle":"<menu> : l'élément de menu - HTML (HyperText Markup Language) | MDN","noIndexing":false}}